{"tid":121834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"已婚文員涉荃灣姦劫鳳姐　待報告下月訊","createTime":"2017-02-15T14:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T14:08:28.000Z","uid":3846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e89b365e166beb3dc2c24623d831fccf61bc74","tid":121834,"uid":3846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:07:06.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】荃灣早前發生姦劫鳳姐案，已婚船務文員梁家威（36歲）涉嫌戴口罩進入荃灣川龍街一單位，亮出一呎長利刀威嚇鳳姐，用尼龍繩綁起鳳姐強姦，再劫去手機逃走。案件今在西九龍法院提堂，被告被控一項強姦罪，暫時毋須答辯，以等候法證報告及法律意見，被告繼續還柙至3月15日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n　　控罪指，被告梁家威於2016年12月1日在荃灣川龍街一單位強姦女子X。<br />\n<br />\n　　法庭記者：潘琪慧"},{"pid":"2a47cea04fe1632e12f21b5daf2db86164cfd2d9","tid":121834,"uid":3910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b51d9983d6edcab8ae33551ddf8b9fd85c0a17","tid":121834,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"老雞都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}